A military General court martial sitting in Abuja has found Major General Hakeem Otiki guilty and ordered his dishonourable dismissal from service among other recommendations over missing funds. Major General Otiki has been facing trial over diversion of funds since 17 September 2019. The General Court Martial headed by Lt Gen Lamidi Adeosun commenced trial on 17 September 2019 at the Nigerian Army Officers Mess Asokoro, Abuja.
The Court last night sentenced the general subject military council approval Details later…